BT 1 0 0 1 0 63 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The AIIT-THRESI Wike Singularity equation -- ERR\(T\) = 1/T + 0.72/T^2.59 -- contains the exponent 2.59 = 1 + 1/nu, where) Tj T* (nu = 0.6298 is the 3D Ising correlation length exponent. This paper proves that the same universality class governs: \(1\) the) Tj T* (Wike coherence phase transition, \(2\) polymer chain collapse at the theta point \(Flory-de Gennes\), and \(3\) tau protein) Tj T* (misfolding in Alzheimer's disease. All three are in the 3D Ising universality class. The Bootstrap reversal \(NIR -) Tj (> coherence) Tj T* (restoration\) should show the same critical exponent 2.59 in its reversal kinetics. This is a quantitative, testable prediction) Tj T* (that connects quantum biology to neurodegeneration physics.) Tj T* ET
